Returns: Bitmask of predefined category sets. Value is either 0 or a combination of @B_android#webkit#TracingConfig#CATEGORIES_NONE_E@, @B_android#webkit#TracingConfig#CATEGORIES_ALL_E@, @B_android#webkit#TracingConfig#CATEGORIES_ANDROID_WEBVIEW_E@, @B_android#webkit#TracingConfig#CATEGORIES_WEB_DEVELOPER_E@, @B_android#webkit#TracingConfig#CATEGORIES_INPUT_LATENCY_E@, @B_android#webkit#TracingConfig#CATEGORIES_RENDERING_E@, @B_android#webkit#TracingConfig#CATEGORIES_JAVASCRIPT_AND_RENDERING_E@, and @B_android#webkit#TracingConfig#CATEGORIES_FRAME_VIEWER_E@
getPredefinedCategories().Description: Returns a bitmask of the predefined category sets of this configuration.

Returns: Empty list if no custom category patterns are specified. This value will never be null.
getCustomIncludedCategories().Description: Returns the list of included custom category patterns for this configuration.

Returns: The tracing mode of this configuration. Value is @B_android#webkit#TracingConfig#RECORD_UNTIL_FULL_E@, or @B_android#webkit#TracingConfig#RECORD_CONTINUOUSLY_E@
getTracingMode().Description: Returns the tracing mode of this configuration.
